<div class="Story">
    We officially met at a dance school here in Auckland, with both of us enrolled in the same Salsa class. What followed were several evenings of coffee and chocolate dates, dance performances, a mutual love of puns, and new hobbies (Mel introduced Art to Harry Potter, and he got her addicted to HearthStone).
